    <title>树莓派3B+设置静态IP</title>
    <link href="https://qishilmx.github.io/2019/02/25/%E6%A0%91%E8%8E%93%E6%B4%BE3B-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81IP/"/>
    <id>https://qishilmx.github.io/2019/02/25/树莓派3B-设置静态IP/</id>
    <published>2019-02-24T16:29:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-02-24T16:30:45.516Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><!-- build time:Mon Feb 25 2019 00:42:29 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><a id="more"></a><p>执行<strong>sudo vim /etc/dhcpcd.conf</strong><br>在文件末尾添加<br><strong>#有线静态ip设置</strong><br><strong>interface eth0</strong><br><strong>static ip_address=192.168.0.53/24</strong> #IPV4的地址<br><strong>static ip6_address=fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::ff/64</strong> #IPV6的地址<br><strong>static routers=192.168.0.1</strong> #网关<br><strong>static domain_name_servers=192.168.0.1 8.8.8.8 fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::1</strong> #DNS<br><strong>#无线静态IP设置</strong><br><strong>interface wlan0</strong><br><strong>static ip_address=192.168.0.53/24</strong> #PV4的地址<br><strong>static ip6_address=fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::ff/64</strong> #IPV6的地址<br><strong>static routers=192.168.0.1</strong> #网关<br><strong>static domain_name_servers=192.168.0.1 8.8.8.8 fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::1</strong> #DNS</p><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
    
